<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>StepSetGo - Lépj egy egészségesebb élet felé!</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../src/css/landing.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../src/css/output.css" />
</head>
<section
  class="relative w-full min-h-screen lg:min-h-[calc(71vh*1.3)] xl:min-h-[calc(81vh*1.3)] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden -top-32"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      src="../src/images/hatter.png"
      alt="Background"
      class="w-full h-full xl:max-w-[70%] object-cover scale-y-[-1]"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-gradient bg-pattern scale-y-[-1]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 xl:hidden">
    <img
      src="../src/images/hattermobile.png"
      alt="Background"
      class="w-full h-full xl:max-w-[70%] object-cover scale-y-[-1]"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-gradient bg-pattern scale-y-[-1]"></div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative z-30 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 -mt-16"
  >
    <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-end">
      <!-- Woman image positioned behind the card -->
      <div
        class="absolute left-0 lg:left-[5%] xl:left-[10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 fade-in hidden lg:block pointer-events-none"
      >
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#76abae]/20 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-2xl"
          ></div>
          <img
            src="../src/images/middleSection.png"
            alt="Edzésterv"
            class="hidden lg:block w-auto h-[550px] lg:h-[720px] xl:h-[720px] drop-shadow-2xl relative scale-110 lg:scale-95 xl:scale-110 xl:rotate-[-28deg] xl:right-34 -top-18 -left-32"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-24 h-24 bg-[#76abae]/10 rounded-full blur-xl"
          ></div>
          <div
            class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-[#76abae]/10 rounded-full blur-xl"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Workout plan card in foreground - shifted right -->
      <div
        class="text-[#EEEEEE] h-auto fade-in bg-gradient-to-br from-[#222831]/95 to-[#1a1f26]/95 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-2xl border border-[#76abae]/30 relative z-20 w-full max-w-xl sm:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl lg:mr-0 xl:mr-8"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-32 bg-[#76abae]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"
        ></div>

        <div class="relative z-50">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-[#76abae] to-[#5a9294] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-[#222831]"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-[#76abae] text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase"
              >Személyre szabott</span
            >
          </div>

          <h2
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight"
          >
            Egyéni
            <span
              class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#76abae] to-[#9ed4d6]"
              >edzésterv</span
            >
          </h2>

          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-[#EEEEEE]/90 leading-relaxed mb-5 max-w-xl"
          >
            Készítsd el saját edzéstervedet, ami tökéletesen illeszkedik az
            életmódodhoz és céljaidhoz. Válaszd ki a gyakorlatokat, állítsd be
            az időtartamot és kövesd nyomon a fejlődésedet.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="group bg-[#222831]/60 rounded-xl p-4 border border-[#76abae]/10 hover:border-[#76abae]/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#222831]/80"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#76abae]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:bg-[#76abae]/20 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76abae]"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                Testreszabható
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#EEEEEE]/70 text-xs">
                Állítsd össze a neked megfelelő gyakorlatokat és
                ismétlésszámokat.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="group bg-[#222831]/60 rounded-xl p-4 border border-[#76abae]/10 hover:border-[#76abae]/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#222831]/80"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#76abae]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:bg-[#76abae]/20 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76abae]"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                Heti ütemezés
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#EEEEEE]/70 text-xs">
                Tervezd meg az egész hetedet előre, hatékonyan.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="group bg-[#222831]/60 rounded-xl p-4 border border-[#76abae]/10 hover:border-[#76abae]/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#222831]/80"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#76abae]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:bg-[#76abae]/20 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76abae]"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                Haladás követés
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#EEEEEE]/70 text-xs">
                Lásd a fejlődésedet részletes statisztikákkal.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="group bg-[#222831]/60 rounded-xl p-4 border border-[#76abae]/10 hover:border-[#76abae]/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#222831]/80"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#76abae]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:bg-[#76abae]/20 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76abae]"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                Gyors kezdés
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#EEEEEE]/70 text-xs">
                Percek alatt elkészítheted az első edzésterved.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a
            href="/plans/view"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#76abae] to-[#5a9294] text-[#222831] font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#76abae]/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <span class="text-base">Edzésterv készítése</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
